  <p>BURS Premium is 109 kr/month or 799 kr/year in Sweden, and €9.99/month or €79.99/year in the rest of the EU. There is no free tier. You can cancel anytime from your account settings or via the App Store / Google Play. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period.</p>

  <h2>3. Acceptable use</h2>
  <p>Don't share your account. Don't try to extract or scrape another user's wardrobe. Don't use BURS to build a competing dataset. Don't upload images you don't have the right to upload.</p>

